                growth as a developer.
            </p>
        </div>

        <div class="about-card">
            <h2>My Journey</h2>
            <p>
                My passion for web development started early in my studies. I discovered the power of creating 
                interactive web experiences and have been constantly improving my skills in front-end and back-end 
                technologies.
            </p>
            <p>
                I'm particularly drawn to modern frameworks like Blazor and .NET, which allow me to build efficient, 
                scalable applications. I believe in continuous learning and staying updated with the latest industry trends.
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>